title: The Collected Angel: After the Fall (2007-11) (Digital) (Empire)
description:
Contains: IDW's "Angel: After the Fall" series and its various spin-off mini-series.

ANGEL - Pseudo-TPBs compiled from the recent digital re-releases by Empire, broken down per creative and/or narrative continuity thusly:
   "After the Fall"     (issues 01-05),   "After the Fall: First Night" (06-08),   
   "After the Fall: Continued" (09-17),   untitled Kelley Armstrong arc (18-22),   
   "After the Fall: Epilogue"  (23),      "Drusilla"                    (24-25),   
   "Boys and Their Toys"       (26-27),   untitled Bill Willingham arc  (28-32),   
   "Connorland"                (33-38),   untitled David Tischman arc   (39-44),   
   and the final issue "Angel Yearbook"

ANGEL: ONLY HUMAN - Spin-off featuring Gunn and Illyria. Five issues compiled into one, original releases by independent scanners.

EDDIE HOPE - A side-story originally serialized in "Angel" 28 thru 39. Includes a full set of variant covers by David Messina, all featuring the character of Eddie.

ILLYRIA: HAUNTED - Spin-off featuring Illyria and introducing Pancakes. Four issues compiled into one, original releases by Minutemen.

SPIKE - Eight issues compiled into one, original releases by Minutemen.
SPIKE: AFTER THE FALL - Four issues compiled into one, ditto.
SPIKE: THE DEVIL YOU KNOW - Four issues compiled into one, ditto.

See <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angel:_After_the_Fall" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angel:_After_the_Fall</a>  for more details.
